340 g Chicken Breasts
14 g Parsley and Cilantro
¾ cup Parboiled Rice
1 unit Lemon
1.5 tsp Cumin-Turmeric Spice Blend
200 g Zucchini
2 unit Green Onion
160 g Sweet Bell Pepper
¾ tsp Garlic Salt
3 tbsp Oil*
¼ tsp Salt and Pepper*
1 tbsp Unsalted Butter*
¼ tsp Sugar*

